OL,3,CThe history of Bluebird K7: How an
OL,4,Cicon was brought back from the depths
OL,6,FWith the return of Donald Campbell's
OL,7,Ficonic craft to Coniston, Bluebird K7
OL,8,Fis now installed as an exhibit in the
OL,9,FRuskin museum.
OL,11,FThis is the latest chapter in a story
OL,12,F70 years in the making for the famous
OL,13,Fhydroplane.
OL,15,FDonald Campbell first set a world
OL,16,Fwater-speed record in the three-point
OL,17,Fboat in 1955 on Ullswater. With her
OL,18,Funusual shape, K7 was often said to
OL,19,Fresemble a large blue lobster by
OL,20,Fonlookers.
