OL,3,CThe history of Bluebird K7: How an
OL,4,Cicon was brought back from the depths
OL,6,FShe was capable of exerting 3500
OL,7,Fpounds of force and would spend the
OL,8,Fcoming decade cementing her place in
OL,9,Frecords history.
OL,11,FOver the next twelve years, skipper
OL,12,Fand boat would go on to set a further
OL,13,Fsix records. Four of these took place
OL,14,Fon Coniston Water. During this time,
OL,15,Fthe water-speed record was pushed from
OL,16,F202mph to 276mph.
