OL,3,CThe history of Bluebird K7: How an
OL,4,Cicon was brought back from the depths
OL,6,FDonald Campbell's final record attempt
OL,7,Fon 4 January 1967 ended in tragedy.
OL,8,FTravelling at well over 300mph,
OL,9,FBluebird left the surface of the lake,
OL,10,Fsomersaulted and plunged into the
OL,11,Fwater, killing Campbell instantly.
OL,13,FFollowing the fatal crash, the wreck
OL,14,Fof K7 would remain in the depths of
OL,15,FConiston Water for more than thirty
OL,16,Fyears.
