OL,3,CThe history of Bluebird K7: How an
OL,4,Cicon was brought back from the depths
OL,6,FEngineer Bill Smith located her after
OL,7,Fyears of searching and in 2001, he and
OL,8,Fhis team raised the boat from the lake
OL,9,Falong with the remains of Donald
OL,10,FCampbell. Mr Smith began The Bluebird
OL,11,FProject, a restoration of the boat to
OL,12,Freturn her to former glory.
OL,14,FIn 2006, Donald's daughter Gina
OL,15,Fdonated Bluebird K7 to Coniston's
OL,16,FRuskin Museum who built a new wing
OL,17,Fspecifically to house the resurrected
OL,18,Fhydroplane.
