OL,3,CThe history of Bluebird K7: How an
OL,4,Cicon was brought back from the depths
OL,6,FHowever, in 2013, The Bluebird Project
OL,7,Fclaimed ownership of the restored
OL,8,Felements of the craft, having invested
OL,9,Fmoney and time into the restoration.
OL,11,FA dispute between the museum and The
OL,12,FBluebird Project would go on for ten
OL,13,Fyears. During this time, the Tyneside
OL,14,Fengineers took K7 to the Isle of Bute
OL,15,Fin Scotland to run in front of a
OL,16,Fcrowd.JIn 2023, the Ruskin Museum took
OL,17,Flegal action against Bill Smith and
OL,18,Fhis team in an effort to gain
OL,19,Fpossession of the boat.
